Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:04.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(392.655,467.001)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.33,0:01:04.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王生意清淡的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:04.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A slow day at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.63,0:01:06.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  快看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.63,0:01:06.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, check this out
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.28,0:01:08.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两块普通的蟹黄堡肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.28,0:01:08.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two ordinary Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.19,0:01:10.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是一旦技艺精湛地投出去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:10.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but when expertly tossed with the skill of a champ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.94,0:01:11.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会变成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.94,0:01:11.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they become
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.38,0:01:15.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,通向痛苦的单程票
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:15.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A one-way ticket to pain
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.30,0:01:20.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起锚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:20.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heave ho
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.22,0:01:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这外面到底怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the devilfish is going on out here?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.70,0:01:24.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间就是金钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.70,0:01:24.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time is money
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你们在浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and if you boys is wasting time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.08,0:01:28.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就是在浪费金钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:28.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then you're wasting money
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.65,0:01:31.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样恶心得很
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:31.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's just sick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.15,0:01:33.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是我们是在做招徕顾客的仪式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:33.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we were performing a ritual to attract customers
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.73,0:01:36.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真要想引到顾客  必须要让咱伤着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:36.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the only way it can work is for us to get hurt
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.42,0:01:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,伤势要很重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.42,0:01:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,real bad
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.32,0:01:39.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪个傻子跟你们说要那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:39.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What stupid barnacle told you that?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.33,0:01:43.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  你们别自残了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:43.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, instead of killing yourselves
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.98,0:01:47.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有非常重要的事情要交给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:47.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got something real important for you to do for me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.88,0:01:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们有没有准备好面对你们的超级
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, are you men ready for your super
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.25,0:01:54.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超级
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:54.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Super"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.84,0:01:56.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:56.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Special
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.42,0:01:58.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:58.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Special"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.40,0:01:59.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:01:59.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Secret
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.55,0:02:01.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:01.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Secret"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.46,0:02:02.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:02.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Assignment
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吊我们胃口了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put us out of our misery
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.66,0:02:08.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要知道  一定要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:08.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta know, I gotta know
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.50,0:02:12.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个要帮我粉刷房子内墙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:12.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The two of you are to paint the inside of me house
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.40,0:02:16.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我得先警告你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:16.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, let me give you two a warning
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.79,0:02:19.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这油漆是永久性的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:19.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This here paint is absolutely permanent
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远都不会脱落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It will never come off
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.78,0:02:28.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是让我看到油漆滴到墙以外的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:28.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so if I see even one drop on anything but wall
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.16,0:02:35.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就割掉你们屁股  挂到我壁炉上面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have your rear ends cut off
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:35.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and mounted over me fireplace
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:34.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(296,230)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:34.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1122,244)}派大星
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.42,0:02:36.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你们干活愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:36.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So have fun with the job
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.01,0:02:39.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:39.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.69,0:02:40.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:40.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.89,0:02:45.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板的珍贵宝物好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:45.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs sure has a lot of expensive treasures
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.08,0:02:46.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,个个都容易滴上油漆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:46.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to drip paint on
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.73,0:02:49.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说该不该把墙上的东西拿下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:49.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think we should take this stuff off the walls?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.86,0:02:51.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不该  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:51.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No way, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.70,0:02:54.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搬东西又不会加工钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:54.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not getting paid to move stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.25,0:02:56.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我们根本就领不到工钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:56.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, we're not getting paid at all
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.06,0:02:57.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的就这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:57.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what I said
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.54,0:02:59.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不领工钱  就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:02:59.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not getting paid, and that's final
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.88,0:03:02.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  那就绕开这些东西刷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:02.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll just paint around all this stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.59,0:03:04.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错  别给我工钱就行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:04.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good, just don't pay me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们首先要铺防水布
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First, we need to set out the tarp
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,防水布来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tarp, ahoy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱还得要再铺些  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to need more coverage, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这样才像话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, that's what I'm talking about
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.09,0:03:18.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们应该得打开这几罐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:18.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we should open these cans of
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永久性油漆了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,permanent paint now
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.33,0:03:23.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种油漆永远都不脱落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:23.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That will never, ever come off
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.51,0:03:25.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是沾上什么别的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:25.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if we get it on anything
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板就会割掉我们的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs will cut our butts off
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.32,0:03:30.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后挂到墙壁上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:30.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And mount them on the wall
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.94,0:03:35.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:35.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Careful, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, careful
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.31,0:03:43.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:43.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Careful, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  盖子已经开完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, the lid's already off
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在轮我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it' my turn
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这罐也让我来开吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should do this one, too, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是劣质
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that was a rip-off
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  准备好刷子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick, let's get our brushes ready
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是先用小一点的刷子好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should start with a smaller brush
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  得开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Patrick, got to get started
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.45,0:04:27.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刷这面墙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:27.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,painting this wall
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要用永久性油漆  不能滴到别的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with the permanent paint that we can't get on anything
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.95,0:04:31.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能刷墙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:31.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but the wall
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.25,0:04:34.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就  开始刷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:34.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, here we go
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,一小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.50,0:04:39.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再让我做会心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:39.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a few more seconds of mental preparation
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就可以开始刷墙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll be painting this wall
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,两小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就要开始刷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm getting to the painting
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.14,0:04:48.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,三小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不能快点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you move it along?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.06,0:04:50.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我转场都用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:50.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm all out of time cards
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here I go
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.95,0:05:18.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:18.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.41,0:05:25.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还会有比大油漆泡泡更糟的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:25.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What could be worse than a giant paint bubble?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.36,0:05:25.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:25.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两个大油漆泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two giant paint bubbles
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.73,0:05:37.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:37.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.52,0:05:38.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咋了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:38.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.98,0:05:40.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这泡泡不能再大下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:40.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think this bubble can get much bigger
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.77,0:05:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡扯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nonsense
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.90,0:05:44.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:44.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat, no
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.25,0:05:58.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:58.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整间房都刷完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We painted the whole house
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且油漆一滴都没沾到墙以外的东
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and without getting a drop of paint on anything but the
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.71,0:06:03.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:03.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flopping flotsam
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.96,0:06:04.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是个什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:04.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.64,0:06:16.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们完蛋了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:16.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're dead, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.23,0:06:17.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道那什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:17.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you know what that is?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是一块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.25,0:06:20.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:20.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I win
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.20,0:06:23.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不单单是一块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:23.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not just a dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.02,0:06:25.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是蟹老板赚到的第一块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:25.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Mr. Krabs's first dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.02,0:06:26.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他最珍贵的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:26.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,his most prized possession
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.79,0:06:28.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们把油漆沾到上面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:28.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And we got paint on it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.32,0:06:31.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你太过激了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:31.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you are overreacting, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没看到有油漆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't see any paint
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.22,0:06:34.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问题不大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:34.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, this isn't a problem
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.97,0:06:36.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许擦掉就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:36.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can just wipe it off
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.12,0:06:39.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  应该行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:39.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, I think I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.09,0:06:47.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下看到油漆了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:47.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I see it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不好  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is not good, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.42,0:06:49.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:49.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is not good
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板马上就要回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs is going to be home soon
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.13,0:06:53.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一旦他看到我们把他第一块钱怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:53.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and when he sees what we did to his dollar
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:54.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(732.084,213.001)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:55.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(675.848,221.002)}派大星
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.77,0:07:01.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:01.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.95,0:07:04.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要把油漆洗掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:04.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all we got to do is wash the paint off
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.44,0:07:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板就不会知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Krabs will never know
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.80,0:07:06.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板说过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:06.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Krabs said
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,管他蟹老板说的什么鬼话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget what Mr. Krabs said
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.54,0:07:11.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定有东西能让油漆脱落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:11.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every paint comes off with something
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.03,0:07:13.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脱落了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:13.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.16,0:07:14.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:14.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.87,0:07:17.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脱落了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:17.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.92,0:07:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.44,0:07:21.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脱落了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:21.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.87,0:07:22.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:22.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.21,0:07:28.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啥都脱不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:28.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing's working
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.20,0:07:29.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:29.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.59,0:07:31.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可不是原始人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:31.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not cavemen
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.96,0:07:34.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们拥有高科技
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:34.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have technology
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.18,0:07:40.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没脱落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:40.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It didn't work
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都要怪蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is all Mr. Krabs' fault
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.53,0:07:45.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是他一开始没把那臭钱挂那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:45.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If he hadn't hung that stupid dollar in the first place
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.99,0:07:49.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这钱明明跟普普通通的一块钱没两样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:48.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's not like it looks any different
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than a regular dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.84,0:07:50.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛要挂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:50.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why hang it?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.88,0:07:53.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便搞个什么旧钱搁墙上不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:53.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You could just stick any old dollar bill up on the wall
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.81,0:07:55.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就看不出来哪有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:55.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one would even know the difference
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你倒也可以掏我钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You might as well just reach into my wallet
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.79,0:08:00.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿出来一块钱  再挂到墙上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:00.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pull out a dollar and put it on the wall
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.21,0:08:01.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱包拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:01.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,take out your wallet
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.67,0:08:04.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道你要拿这干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:04.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't see where you're going with this
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.96,0:08:05.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:05.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们屁股保住了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our butts are saved, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.64,0:08:08.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我们得要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:08.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now all we have to
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.68,0:08:09.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:09.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, no
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:11.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(938.956,148.999)}糖果
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, no
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:23.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1073.524,785)}投币
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.58,0:08:13.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你投什么投
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:13.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did you put it?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快取  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grab it, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.09,0:08:15.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,取出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:15.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,grab it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.59,0:08:16.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧  赶紧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:16.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.85,0:08:20.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:20.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get it, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.39,0:08:21.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿啊拿啊拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:21.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get it, get it, get it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.94,0:08:28.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来一口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:28.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Want a bite?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  还有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, we still got time
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要恐惧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't panic, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.06,0:08:33.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐惧就是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:33.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,panic is the enemy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.03,0:08:33.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你很强大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:33.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are strong
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.94,0:08:35.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以用你的力量克服的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:35.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Through your strength you shall overcome
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.24,0:08:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己看着办吧  好哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're on your own, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.19,0:08:45.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把蟹老板的钱挂回墙上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:45.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,put the dollar back on the wall
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.95,0:08:46.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:46.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.38,0:08:49.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:49.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.27,0:08:51.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完工了  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:51.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're all done, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可好看了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything looks great
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.35,0:08:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  你看都没必要看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you don't have to look around
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们已经帮你看完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We already did that for you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.72,0:09:00.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个好像有什么见不得人的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:09:00.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You both look like you got a dirty little secret
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.39,0:09:03.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:03.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm kidding
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.07,0:09:04.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看下你们的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:04.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see how you did
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.90,0:09:05.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错啊  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:05.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not bad, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.98,0:09:06.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:06.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not bad
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,粉刷平整  富有光泽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A nice even coat, high gloss
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毫无起泡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no bubbles
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.78,0:09:12.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊真好看  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:12.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, looks great, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll just be going
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.07,0:09:16.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼  看你们干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:16.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flipping fish parcels, look what you did
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别割我们屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please don't cut off our butts
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Krabs, I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.79,0:09:21.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:21.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Sorry?"
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.59,0:09:23.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们给我的小摆设都除尘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:23.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You dusted all my knickknacks
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was really nice
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great Barrier Reef
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.27,0:09:28.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这啥东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:28.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能怪我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not our fault
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.55,0:09:31.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想没屁股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:31.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be buttless
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.13,0:09:36.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踢脚线的漆多半是它自个刷上去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I suppose the floor molding
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just painted itself on its own
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.18,0:09:39.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才叫好手艺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:39.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what I call craftsmanship
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.31,0:09:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Criminy jim jam
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.43,0:09:45.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你弄到了我的前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:45.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You messed up my dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.27,0:09:46.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面的娃娃架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:46.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,rama
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.77,0:09:52.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,娃娃架上面的娃娃原先排得特整齐的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:50.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All the dolls in this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:52.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,dollarama were perfectly aligned
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.73,0:09:54.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:54.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mama
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们居然还以为我注意不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you boys thought I wouldn't notice
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.61,0:09:59.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过倒也没造成什么损失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:09:59.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I guess no harm done
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们几个可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, boys, you're free to go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.54,0:10:03.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:03.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's funny
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.59,0:10:05.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不记得有这么一大叠画
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:05.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't remember a stack of paintings
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.37,0:10:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叠在我放第一块钱的墙上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,jutting from the wall where me first dollar used to be
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.30,0:10:11.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实我根本就不记得有这么一幅画
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:11.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, I don't remember this painting at all
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.17,0:10:16.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这幅也不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:16.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or this one
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.59,0:10:20.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:20.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.72,0:10:22.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是那个  到处闲晃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:22.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, just hanging around
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:22.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(953,920)}挂 着
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.82,0:10:23.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:23.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boo
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站地上来  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get down onto the floor, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在硬要当傻子也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, now you're just being silly
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.94,0:10:33.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:33.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, no
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.32,0:10:33.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:33.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't look
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.82,0:10:34.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:34.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a trick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.83,0:10:39.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们把我第一块钱沾得都是油漆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:39.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you two get paint all over me first dollar?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.97,0:10:42.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:42.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're so sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.03,0:10:47.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后你们就用蜡笔在上面乱画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:47.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then did you draw on it with crayon?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以为  人家可能会买账
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought, you know, maybe he'd buy it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.47,0:10:55.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:55.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道我得干什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what I've got to do now?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说我们屁股吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean, our butts?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.23,0:11:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能最后再用一遍屁股吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I use mine one last time?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以了  完好如初
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There we go, good as new
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.92,0:11:13.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我骗你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:13.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I lied
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种油漆其实碰到口水就能脱落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This paint actually comes off with saliva
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.11,0:11:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我懂了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get it, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.77,0:11:20.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你骗我们这种油漆是永久性的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:20.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You told us the paint was permanent
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样我跟派大星就会更加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so me and Patrick would be more careful
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.74,0:11:24.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不让油漆沾到别的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:24.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and not get paint on anything
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.53,0:11:27.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错  我只是喜欢整你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:27.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah, I just like to mess with you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,姜还是老的辣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The old man's still got it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crud
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.07,0:11:52.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话得用正常说的  不能到处乱喷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:52.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really got to learn to say it, not spray it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:56.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs101.25\pos(720,793.001)}蟹堡王培训视频
