Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.33,0:12:14.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎你的加入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:14.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome aboard
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.53,0:12:16.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你正在观看本视频
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:16.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you're watching this video
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就让我第一个对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then let me be the first to say
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,525)}恭喜你
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.09,0:12:22.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你已经被蟹堡王餐厅录用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:20.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've recently been hired
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:22.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by The Krusty Krab Restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是你正式培训的第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and this is your first official day of training
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在可以做蟹黄堡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I make a Krabby Patty now?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.55,0:12:28.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  你还得学不少东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:28.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, you've got a lot to learn
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.76,0:12:31.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才可以去做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:31.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before you're ready to make a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.32,0:12:32.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正如图表所示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:32.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As you can see by this graph
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:36.31,注释,,0,0,0,,[ graph（图表）与 giraffe（长颈鹿）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.19,0:12:36.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,图表
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:36.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Graph
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.73,0:12:37.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,录用你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:37.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are now employed
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.73,0:12:41.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是全裤头村最成功的餐厅之一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by one of the most successful restaurants
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:41.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:46.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(344.452,521.001)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是这并非是一夜之内做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it didn't get that way overnight
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.65,0:12:46.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为六点钟就关店了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:46.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because the store closes at 6:00
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王之所以能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, story of The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.42,0:12:52.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关键就在于店长勤奋刻苦  坚毅不拔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:52.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is a story of one man's hard work, perseverance
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.01,0:12:53.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,志向远大  矢志不渝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:53.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,vision, determination
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.57,0:12:54.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挥洒汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:54.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and sweat
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汗水最关键
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But mostly his sweat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(609.568,1025.001)}白手起家
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.75,0:13:02.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可能会想  尤金蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:02.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You may think Mr. Eugene H. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.19,0:13:04.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王公司的所有者及创办者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:04.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,owner and founder of Krusty Krab Inc.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:07.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(991.176,357.001)}汽水
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至今一直都是金融鬼才
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has always been the financial wizard he is today
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想得对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you're right
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,战后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After the war
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.28,0:13:21.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板深陷无尽的抑郁  与世隔绝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:19.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs stayed secluded in a deep depression
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that seemed endless
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但后来他大幅转运
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But then his luck changed
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收购了一家破产的养老院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when he acquired a bankrupt retirement home
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.47,0:13:28.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,作了几处细微的改变之后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:28.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and with a few minor alterations
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab was born
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(858.618,701.001)}蟹堡亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:30.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(858.618,701.001)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听上去好像有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a lot of
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.75,0:13:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hoopla
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.25,0:13:37.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听上去好像有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:37.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a lot
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.71,0:13:38.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:38.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hoopla
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.98,0:13:40.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听上去好像有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:40.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hoopla
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hoopla
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听上去好像要讲很多废话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a lot of hoopla
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才能移交一个小蟹黄堡的所有权对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to make over a little Krabby Patty, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.72,0:13:50.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:50.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:53.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,1021.001)}今天的蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:54.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(205.868,353)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1202.065,220.999)}藤壶漂白液
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:57.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(595.509,555.001)}垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:13:58.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(707.983,801)}严禁续杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:13:59.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(790.33,254.999)}菜单
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.27,0:14:02.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为跟上现在顾客的日益提高的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:02.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To keep up with today's demanding customers
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.81,0:14:04.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不惜一切代价
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:04.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no expense has been spared
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.19,0:14:07.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,采购一切最新快餐科技成就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:06.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to acquire all the latest achievements
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in fast-food technology
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.91,0:14:10.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个是增强型肉饼控制装置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:10.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This here is an advanced patty-control mechanism
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.12,0:14:14.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边是我们的自动金钱处理系统
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:14.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you see our automated money-handling system
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.06,0:14:14.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准摸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:14.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't touch
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.93,0:14:17.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些是高质量饮料温度调控设备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:17.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are high-quality beverage temperature devices
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.62,0:14:18.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进口的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:18.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Imported
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.33,0:14:21.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个是液体转移机的原型机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:21.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This here's a prototype liquid transfer machine
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.84,0:14:24.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:24.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And most importantly
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:28.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(541.28,365)}蟹堡王番茄酱
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.15,0:14:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以拿到最先进的散装调味品单位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you get your state-of-the-art
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,condiment-dispersal units
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.26,0:14:29.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要不就买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:29.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now are you going to buy something
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.26,0:14:31.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不就光站这然后付占地费
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:31.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or just stand there 'cause there's a standing fee
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.10,0:14:35.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些现代化设备似乎把你看晕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All of this modernization
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:35.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,seems a little overwhelming doesn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.15,0:14:36.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:36.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, luckily for you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.52,0:14:39.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板十分害怕机器人统治
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:39.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs' fear of robot overlords
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,便时刻维持着科技的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,keeps the balance of technology in check
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.91,0:14:45.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过如果说现代化是蟹堡王的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:45.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But if modernization is the heart of The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.09,0:14:48.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么员工就是肝和胆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:48.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then employees are the liver and gallbladder
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.20,0:14:50.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看你有没有相应的素质
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:50.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see if you've got what it takes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.66,0:14:53.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,沉着  自信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:53.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,poised, confident
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.47,0:14:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑容仿佛在说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a smile that says
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.87,0:14:57.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世界你好  我能为你点餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:57.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Hello, world, may I take your order?"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.62,0:15:01.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能成为一个好员工  海绵宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:58.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got the makings
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:01.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of a good employee, Mr. SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过对每个好员工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But for every good employee
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.47,0:15:05.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总会有个不成器的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.47,0:15:05.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's one who is not so good
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.67,0:15:06.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:06.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不专心  不耐心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,inattentive, impatient
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.83,0:15:10.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,目光呆滞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:10.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a glazed look in the eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.99,0:15:12.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,仔细看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:12.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look carefully at the
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.14,0:15:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,写着  我真希望自己不在这的胸牌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"I Really Wish I Weren't Here Right Now" button
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.64,0:15:17.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种员工都有一个外号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:17.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a name for employees like this
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.23,0:15:20.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们都叫他  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:20.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but we'll call him Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这回会有加班费了吧  对吧蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm getting paid overtime for this, right, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.19,0:15:25.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:25.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, can't hear you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:27.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(428.764,913)}培训
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是说我现在要去做蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does this mean I get to make a Krabby Patty now?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  你要做蟹黄堡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you can't make a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得要先理解一个字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without understanding the phrase
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:47.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(776.271,565)}屎
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.78,0:15:35.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:35.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"POOP"?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.74,0:15:37.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一旦理解了屎的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:37.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once you understand POOP
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.79,0:15:40.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就能理解你在蟹堡王的地位了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:40.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll understand your place at The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.55,0:15:42.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是屎是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:42.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what does POOP mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.75,0:15:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实是一段精心编写的代码
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's actually a carefully organized code
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.72,0:15:47.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,仔细看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:47.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch closely
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:55.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1008.834,195.001)}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:55.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1008.834,403)}都点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:55.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.907,631.001)}我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:55.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.907,841.001)}蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.84,0:15:52.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:52.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,POOP
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来海绵宝宝先生理解了屎的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like Mr. SquarePants understands POOP
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.98,0:15:57.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了一位典型的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:57.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's a typical customer
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.74,0:15:59.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道他要点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:15:59.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he wants
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.37,0:16:03.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但只要记住屎字  即可迎刃而解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:03.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if we just remember POOP, we can figure it out
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to order
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.11,0:16:06.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得他要点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:06.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think he's going to order
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.48,0:16:11.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fnArial\pos(370,400)}A{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}  沙发
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.98,0:16:11.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fnArial\pos(370,730)}B{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}  昂贵的发型
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fnArial\pos(370,942)}C{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}  蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.45,0:16:12.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:12.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One patty, please
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屎啊  你从来没让我们失望过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,POOP, you never let us down
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你理解了屎的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that you understand POOP
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.28,0:16:21.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想必你觉得自己准备好去做蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:21.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet you think you're ready to make a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别着急  勤奋的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not so fast, Eager McBeaver
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.43,0:16:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还没谈到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We haven't even talked about
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(768.236,791.001)}个人卫生
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.01,0:16:37.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王的每一名员工
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:37.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every employee of The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:45.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(284.198,133)}请洗鳍
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.18,0:16:40.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须执行一套严格的个人卫生准则
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,must comply with a strict set
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:40.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of personal hygiene guidelines
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.23,0:16:42.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:42.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mr. SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.83,0:16:44.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要做好上班准备了没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:44.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are you ready to prepare for your shift?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.31,0:16:48.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好员工总是把自己的手擦得干干净净
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:48.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A good employee always scrubs his hands thoroughly
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要把指甲里面洗干净
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be sure to get under those fingernails
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也别忘了关节
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't forget about the knuckles
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.32,0:16:58.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要确保手心一尘不染
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:58.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And make sure those palms are squeaky clean
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  看看洗好的手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, let's see those hands
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,深入细致
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, that's thorough
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.21,0:17:08.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确保了你的脚擦得锃亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:08.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After making sure your feet are polished
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.34,0:17:11.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脸上没有疤痕和疖子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:11.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your face is clear of any blemishes or boils
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,头发干净整洁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and your hair is neat and tidy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.55,0:17:20.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你准备好要开启全新一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:20.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you are ready to start the day
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.15,0:17:23.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来看看章鱼哥是怎么准备上班的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:23.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let's see how Squidward prepares for his shift
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.85,0:17:32.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记住  员工都不可以成为章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:32.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember, no employee wants to be a Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.69,0:17:34.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你干净又卫生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:34.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that you're clean and hygienic
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.54,0:17:37.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想必你觉得自己准备好去做蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:37.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll bet you think you're ready to make that Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.49,0:17:40.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:40.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.12,0:17:45.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:45.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoa, there
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.06,0:17:47.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还有好几个话题要先讲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:47.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We still have a few more topics to cover first
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(846.568,989)}你的工作环境
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.54,0:17:53.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保持工作环境干净整洁特别重要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:52.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's important to keep your area tidy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:53.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and free of droppings
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.26,0:17:58.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但工作环境整洁只是工作的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:58.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But a clean workstation is only part of the job
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.39,0:18:00.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要把脑中的想象化为现实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:00.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To make the vision in your head a reality
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要物质的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll need supplies
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.43,0:18:04.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好员工总是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:04.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a good employee always
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把他的物质支持安排得井井有条
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,keeps his supplies well-organized
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.24,0:18:11.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常好  海绵宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:11.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very nice, Mr. SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.39,0:18:13.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,物质各得其所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:13.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not a pickle out of place
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.65,0:18:16.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看章鱼哥是怎么打理工作环境的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:16.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let's see how Squidward keeps his workstation
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:18.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(609.568,975)}请勿打扰
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝先生可以顶替你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. SquarePants can cover for you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.97,0:18:30.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你的工作环境正常运作了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:30.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that your workstation is up and running
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.11,0:18:30.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能你觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:30.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,perhaps you think
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.93,0:18:33.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你准备好去做举世闻名的蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:33.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're ready to make the world-famous Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别急
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Calm down
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有好多的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's plenty of time left
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.15,0:18:42.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还得确保你准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:42.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to make sure you're ready
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.76,0:18:44.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工作的精神方面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:44.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the psychological aspect of the job
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:48.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,717.001)}与老板谈话
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我能加工资吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, can I have a raise?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.98,0:18:51.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:51.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做得好  海绵宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good job, Mr. SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.75,0:18:55.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在可以做蟹黄堡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:55.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I make a Krabby Patty now?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.15,0:18:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我们从幕后走到前线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now we move
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from behind the scenes to the front lines
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.22,0:19:02.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在此考察工作中最重要的方面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:00.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where we'll examine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:02.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the most important aspect of the industry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.66,0:19:03.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:03.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the customer
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.81,0:19:06.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者照我们的说法是  蟹堡客
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:06.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or, as we like to say, the "Krustomer"
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.79,0:19:07.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:07.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you a ghost?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.27,0:19:12.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正如动物体内极其珍贵的血液一般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:12.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like precious, precious blood in an animal
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.01,0:19:15.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顾客让蟹堡王生机勃勃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:14.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,customers are what keeps The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:15.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,strong and alive
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.34,0:19:19.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你天花板在跟我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:19.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, your ceiling is talking to me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是要来点餐的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you going to order something
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是要来跟天花板交朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or just make friends with the paneling?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.81,0:19:26.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:26.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have an uh
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.32,0:19:35.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:35.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.83,0:19:38.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  别在这里发癫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:38.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, go be stupid somewhere else
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  记住蟹老板说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, remember what Mr. Krabs says
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1025.32,673)}金钱永远是对的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天花板说得对  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The ceiling is right, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.64,0:19:48.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就不是个什么好员工
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:48.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're not a very good employee
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.88,0:19:49.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:49.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.61,0:19:51.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以给你点餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:51.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I please take your order?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.26,0:19:59.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们等会再来看这两个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:19:59.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll check in with these two later
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.19,0:20:02.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  我们重点要来讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:02.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right now, it's important that we discuss an
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:04.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,817)}紧急情况
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.97,0:20:07.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正如亚特兰蒂斯失落的黄金
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:07.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like the lost gold of Atlantis
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.04,0:20:10.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很多人把蟹黄堡当作财宝看待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:10.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,many consider their Krabby Patty to be a treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至于每样财宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And as with every treasure
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.76,0:20:13.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都会有小偷来偷盗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:13.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's a thief ready to steal it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.91,0:20:16.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你要负责警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:16.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So it's up to you to be the watchful eyes of
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.07,0:20:17.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:17.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.57,0:20:23.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是蟹老板的商业竞争对手  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:23.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Mr. Krabs' business rival, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.14,0:20:26.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃灰去吧  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:26.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat my microscopic dust, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.66,0:20:29.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的秘密配方终于是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:29.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your secret formula is finally mine
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.97,0:20:31.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在偷秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:31.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's stealing the formula
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.63,0:20:34.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要怎么办  海绵宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:34.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Mr. SquarePants?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你永远也抓不到我的  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never catch me, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.81,0:20:48.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经换到最大超速档了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:48.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not when I shift into maximum overdrive
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.10,0:20:54.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早知道就装涡轮增压器了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:54.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew I should've gotten the turbo
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.02,0:20:59.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:20:59.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hear me, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.59,0:21:01.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要想从我这拿走这个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:01.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll take this Krabby Patty from me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.61,0:21:04.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少也要先让我死透了再
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:04.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you pry it from my cold, dead
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.45,0:21:14.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到这  又一个紧急危机解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:14.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And so another emergency is avoided
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.06,0:21:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多亏有海绵宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thanks to Mr. SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.33,0:21:18.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们再来看看章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:18.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's check in on Squidward again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.42,0:21:21.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:21.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.07,0:21:23.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要记住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:23.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just remember
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:24.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(422.782,493)}屎
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.76,0:21:27.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我给你个建议
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:27.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, if I could make a suggestion
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.38,0:21:30.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不你点个蟹黄堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:30.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why don't you just order a Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好办法  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great idea, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.90,0:21:35.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:35.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty, please
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.89,0:21:36.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,堂食还是外带
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:36.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that for here or to go?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.28,0:21:43.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别泄气  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:43.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.72,0:21:45.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都是分内之事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:45.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's all part of the job
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:51.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(673.839,241)}培训指南
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.11,0:21:48.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然培训的基础知识都学完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:48.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that we've covered all the basics of your training
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.64,0:21:51.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么该到了你迫切等待的时刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:51.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's time for the moment you've been waiting for
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.94,0:22:25.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,制作蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:25.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Preparing the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.53,0:22:29.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每个伟大王朝的中央都有耀眼的王冠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:29.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At the center of every great dynasty is the crown jewel
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:30.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1061.472,579.001)}蟹黄堡  蟹堡王独家
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.35,0:22:31.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保持着王朝的兴旺与发达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:31.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which keeps it alive and thriving
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.70,0:22:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对于蟹堡王  这个王冠就是蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For The Krusty Krab, this is the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.87,0:22:39.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而现在的你  这份工作里的小小员工
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.87,0:22:39.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now you, the humble employee off the street
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.93,0:22:43.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让这份生意得以维持的必备人力资源
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.93,0:22:42.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the all-too-necessary human resource
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:43.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that keeps this business afloat
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.87,0:22:46.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,将会学到一份神圣又黑暗的秘诀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.87,0:22:46.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will learn the sacred and dark secrets
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.38,0:22:49.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,指引你亲手制作蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:49.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of how to prepare, with your very own hands
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.26,0:22:52.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那奢华的  那让你嘴唇湿润
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:52.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sumptuous, lip-moistening
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.87,0:22:56.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,背脊刺痛  心脏停跳的兴奋中枢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.87,0:22:56.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,spine-tingling, heart-stopping pleasure center
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.60,0:22:58.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正是蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:58.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that is a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.53,0:22:59.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.53,0:22:59.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.23,0:23:02.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:02.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.32,0:23:07.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好  秘密配方就是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.32,0:23:07.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, the secret formula
